      <title>拜登支持者在周末疯狂竞选中拒绝辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/biden-loyalists-dismiss-calls-to-quit-in-frenetic-weekend-blitz</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在辩论中表现惨淡，遭到捐助者、顾问、官员和媒体的强烈反对，他们呼吁拜登退出 2024 年大选。拜登的竞选团队正在对此进行反击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/biden-loyalists-dismiss-calls-to-quit-in-frenetic-weekend-blitz</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 22:11:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国央行与政府之间的斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/tensions-grow-between-thailand-central-bank-and-government-on-growth-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行行长一直在反击政客要求降低利率的行为，他对那些感受到压力的同行们说：这不是你们的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/tensions-grow-between-thailand-central-bank-and-government-on-growth-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非总统拉马福萨新内阁成员名单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/who-s-who-in-south-african-president-ramaphosa-s-new-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨任命了一个包括反对党成员在内的内阁，这些反对党成员同意在 5 月 29 日的选举未能产生绝对胜利者后加入执政联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/who-s-who-in-south-african-president-ramaphosa-s-new-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 21:40:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京访问后朝鲜发射导弹展示武力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/north-korea-fires-missile-in-show-of-force-after-putin-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据韩联社报道，朝鲜周一发射一枚疑似弹道导弹，几天前朝鲜发射了一枚火箭，测试了一种可发动核打击的新型多弹头系统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/north-korea-fires-missile-in-show-of-force-after-putin-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 21:18:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非反对派首次入选拉马福萨团结内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/south-africa-elections-opposition-makes-debut-in-ramaphosa-s-unity-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统拉马福萨宣布新内阁，将部长职位分配给反对党政客，同时保留亲密盟友埃诺克·戈东瓦纳担任财政部长，这表明其经济政策的连续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/south-africa-elections-opposition-makes-debut-in-ramaphosa-s-unity-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 20:19:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国极右翼领导人将勒庞在法国的胜利视为典范</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/german-far-right-leader-sees-le-pen-victory-in-france-as-a-model</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国右翼选择党联合领导人艾丽丝·魏德尔表示，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟在法国立法选举首轮中获胜，值得效仿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/german-far-right-leader-sees-le-pen-victory-in-france-as-a-model</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 20:17:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚总统为处理致命青年抗议事件辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/kenyan-president-defends-handling-of-deadly-youth-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托为其部署军队平息过去两周全国范围内抗议活动的决定进行辩护，抗议活动已造成至少 24 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/kenyan-president-defends-handling-of-deadly-youth-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 18:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞领导的极右翼赢得法国第一轮大选并瞄准多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/le-pen-s-far-right-party-projected-to-come-first-in-french-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙和她的其他对手开始制定策略阻止极右翼政党掌权之际，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟在法国立法选举第一轮中占据主导地位，并将目光瞄准了绝对多数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/le-pen-s-far-right-party-projected-to-come-first-in-french-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 18:01:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民意调查显示选民担忧 拜登党内盟友关系趋于紧密</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/top-biden-party-allies-close-ranks-as-poll-signals-voter-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项民意调查显示，拜登上周在与唐纳德·特朗普的辩论中表现不佳，这让更多美国人对总统的领导能力产生了怀疑，因此民主党核心人士纷纷支持拜登竞选连任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-30/top-biden-party-allies-close-ranks-as-poll-signals-voter-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2024 14:36:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登要求捐助者在灾难性的辩论后继续捐款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/biden-seeks-to-reassure-anxious-donors-at-nyc-region-fundraisers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在纽约汉普顿向腰缠万贯的捐助者表示，他承认对自己与唐纳德·特朗普辩论的表现感到担忧，并发誓要坚持竞选连任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-29/biden-seeks-to-reassure-anxious-donors-at-nyc-region-fundraisers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 16:44:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
